comments: I thought I would learn of Aristotle, platos. nero etc. I didn\'t. would I take him again ?? yes I would. he showed us that everyone has an opinion. deal with it. if that was his teachings then I am open minded now and grateful for his knowledge and wisdom. I thought he was the janitor at times. great guy

Philosophy ... Probably the best teacher and class you can ever take. Had the most fun I have ever in any class. Very fun lectures. Even more interesting discussions. Follow the rules, and you will get an A ... simple as that.
